label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"肉鸡肿头综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"禽肺病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":36,"end":41,"text":"脸肿综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"面部肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"肉仔鸡头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"面部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 肉鸡肿头综合征是由禽肺病毒和其他细菌感染引起肉仔鸡头、面部肿胀，所以又叫脸肿综合征。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"肉鸡肿头综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"肉仔鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 肉鸡肿头综合征多发生于4～7周龄肉仔鸡，蛋鸡也有发生，雏鸡和成年鸡均有感染。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"头部肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"皮下组织水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"胶样浸润","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":36,"text":"干酪样物贮留","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"头部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"脸部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"眼睛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"皮下组织","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡头部肿胀，脸部及眼睛周围皮下组织水肿，或胶样浸润，有时有干酪样物贮留。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"髯也肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"扭颈","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"抽搐","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"神经症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":13,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":2,"end":3,"text":"髯","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":0,"end":1,"text":"冠","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 冠、髯也肿胀。有时出现扭颈、抽搐等神经症状。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"通风换气","labels":["control"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"注意光照","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"低密度饲养","labels":["control"]},{"start":37,"end":42,"text":"清洁的垫料","labels":["control"]}]
text: 加强饲养管理，及时通风换气，减少舍内氨气，注意光照，低密度饲养，使用干燥、清洁的垫料等综合措施，可大大降低发病率。

label: [{"start":1,"end":9,"text":"火鸡鼻气管弱毒苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":10,"end":13,"text":"灭活苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":23,"end":30,"text":"肉鸡肿头综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"免疫接种","labels":["control"]}]
text: 用火鸡鼻气管弱毒苗和灭活苗免疫接种，可有效预防肉鸡肿头综合征的发生。

label: [{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"磺胺类","labels":["drug"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"抗菌药物","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 发病后针对继发感染，可应用磺胺类等抗菌药物进行治疗，可控制疫情，降低死亡率。
